<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">Easy.. Go next door and take on those aviaks bigger brothers the Aviak town, and if you want i would suggest trying to get the Hermit in SK at all costs.. he drops best loot around for his lvl (20 every time) he drops Fine Steel weapons and up to 3pp in cash.   Plus great exp and non agro.. unless you are a necro.. all you have to do is walk up to the stone walls at -5500, -2500 in South Karana go in and go to the back of the house.. put your face in the right corner of the chimeny and the wall and say "kill you" he will jump you from there.. he is an exactly 3 min spawn so you can kill fast as you want.  Have fun<hr>Khammion Soulgrasper<br>
