<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">Solo the tex mex gnolls in SK near Paw.  I was and the exp was CRAZY.  just hit them with fire bolt (or whatever the level 20 one is...i dont use it anymore) twice before they are even to you, then send your earth pet in and run around until it gets rooted, then bolt it again.  Be sure you get a SoW, though as it can be difficult (but possible) without it.  I recommend using just the bolt until ~29 because the gnolls seem to have extremely low fire resist.  Good hunting!</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
