<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">If you want to solo, i will give you a few tips.  First, 15 seconds before your pet die tell him to follow you, then summon up a new pet. Type /pet get lost but don't press enter. At the hair second b4 you finish the spell press enter.  This will take the old pet away and get you a newer one with full health.  The second tips is that get a sow before you engage into battle and kite the monster.  Only do it in a wide area.  I recommand an earth pet for this.  Pull it with the strongest bolt spell you have and another DD b4 it gets to you.  Let the pet attack it and send it into the taunt range.  Now, stand back and cast a really strong spell to that monster so that it comes towards you.  Run around until your pet taunts it again.  DO NOT LET IT HURT YOU.  Repeat that till the monster is dead. And if youre oom just sit and med a few feet away from the monster, watch the pet's health tho.<p>

Hope that will help you</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
