<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">Do Not Use Earth Pet for kiting !  They will root and then you lose the advantage of kiting because now the monster is beating up the pet.  If you really want to try it, use water.  It will hack at the monster, cast DD's, and has plenty of hp for when the mob does turn and attack it.  That is when you send another bolt at the mob and then start running again.<p>

And yes, you need Sow or Jboots ;)</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
